    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>《Dark and Quispy》是一款肉鸽（roguelike）生存游戏，具有 2.5D 纸张般的视觉效果。</strong></u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/3a0bc028b80a56a6b5d985dfd9fd3265.poster.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/3a0bc028b80a56a6b5d985dfd9fd3265.webm?t=1728014200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/5f374a733f72bbf0f9f2586a2c253ba7.webp?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=39 /></span>黑暗与危险笼罩的世界，不祥血月将恶毒光芒投射到大地。你可能已经猜到厄运降世。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嗯，你说得对……尤其是对于主火焰。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在最近血月期，无数生物无情地攻击她，她失去了灵魂！她的灵魂被剥夺了，散落在风中，她站在被遗忘的边缘。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为灵魂火焰人民的守护者，这个重任落在了你的身上。只有深入黑暗之心，与凶猛的敌人作战，夺回主火焰失落的灵魂，世界才能恢复平衡   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/a6fd67b9fc78ab59399ae9fb7b95a6a1.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=182 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>武器</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须以某种方式击败敌人！装备强大的武器来击败敌人并尽可能延长生存时间。从被击败的敌人身上收集灵魂火焰来升级你的武器库，使你的武器更强大！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/ee91649b77a549f089998ac1d8f17e28.poster.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/ee91649b77a549f089998ac1d8f17e28.webm?t=1728014200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/2e4c2ca91b9ad685ff1d090dc4b526b0.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=181 /></span><u><i><strong>事件</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅程中，你需要留意随机出现的特殊事件。完成这些挑战即可获得宝贵奖励！但要小心——敌人不会让你轻易获胜，因此谨慎行事，以免丧命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/2c12a177a96c83beb8abd584ebd13a1e.poster.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/2c12a177a96c83beb8abd584ebd13a1e.webm?t=1728014200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/41e0f8b9b3fd47e8a2e0711af0aaa1b0.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=182 /></span><u><i><strong>模组</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过为武器应用模组来增强你的战斗策略！每个模组都会带来独特的效果，让你能够更有效地管理并征服敌人。发现与特定武器协同的强大组合。释放你的创造力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/7a5f4c8134d7104787fe36856fa071b2.poster.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/7a5f4c8134d7104787fe36856fa071b2.webm?t=1728014200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/ef6c0c5e3bb033f1c9c58fdeb4be4e04.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=182 /></span><u><i><strong>升级</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄金是任务中的宝贵资源，一定要明智地使用！抵制购买太多武器的诱惑。相反，保存你的黄金以升级 Quispy 的属性，确保你能在未来的游戏中取得更大的进步。冒险越深，发现的黄金就越多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/94bd8e2a63d1093d097af7ab1a5a239f.poster.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/94bd8e2a63d1093d097af7ab1a5a239f.webm?t=1728014200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/e8c36f0d2abfda60ed800bf6f7a9a7b8.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=181 /></span><u><i><strong>逃撤</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血月升起！是时候撤回营地了！在这个不祥时刻，敌人会变得越来越危险。迅速逃跑，保护你辛苦赚来的黄金！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/9894c7ef45d1f4869aba96dbe7d5c672.poster.avif?t=1728014200\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260360/extras/9894c7ef45d1f4869aba96dbe7d5c672.webm?t=1728014200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
